<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/55" title="View user profile.">oirfid</a> on Monday, April 19, 2004 - 17:29</small><br /><br />
The Half-Life single player mod Nihilst is recruitng team members.  They are currently looking for level designers, modelers, programers, voice actors, and a web designer.  If you are interested please read the teams help wanted post in the RUST forums <a href="http://forums.gamedesign.net/viewtopic.php?t=6199">here</a>.
<br><br>
<center>
<img src="http://www.gamedesign.net/miniwood/images/Nihilist2.jpg" >
</center>
<br><br>
Normally here at RUST we don't like to promote individual mods as many eventually whither and die. However, the Nihilist team has shown that they are a dedicated and hard working team.
