</div><br />


<!-- Node: "QuakeCon Registration Underway" -->
<div class="body_box_header">QuakeCon Registration Underway</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/8" title="View user profile.">Jherax</a> on Thursday, April 15, 2004 - 10:40</small><br /><br />
Registration for the QuakeCon event in Grapevine, TX is underway and anyone interested who hasn't registered for the event can do so online at the <a href="http://www.quakecon.org/">QuakeCon websites</a>. This years event will be at the Gaylord Texan Resort and Convention Center and is supposed to pack an even bigger BYOC and be a weekend full of all sorts of random gaming-related events and whatnot.<br />
<br />
I'm registered and planning to attend, anyone else from the RUST Community planning on being there? Post in the comments if you're planning on attending and maybe we'll have to have a RUST gath
<br /><br />
